{"tid":2044781,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"網傳中印軍爆衝突   解放軍遭拳打腳踢帶走","createTime":"2020-05-31T10:22:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-01T06:05:56.000Z","uid":79563,"like":122,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":52,"replies":[{"pid":"a5e4efe75f513a99e795ffb17b7b4371371726b3","tid":2044781,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:22:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/mWA4Th7btcZQkjjbIxY_8w--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-05/1052ddf0-a30d-11ea-8fd6-be61f4f8d2ac\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FmWA4Th7btcZQkjjbIxY_8w--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-05%2F1052ddf0-a30d-11ea-8fd6-be61f4f8d2ac&h=203e10d9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n周日（31日）在Twitter流傳一段影片顯示，疑似有解放軍與印度軍人在中印邊境地區班公湖（Pangong Tso）發生衝突，一名解放軍被按倒在地，多名印度軍人用木棍等破壞東風猛士偵察車。美媒同日報道稱，解放軍日前在邊境與印度軍人對峙，雙方沒有開火，均有軍人受傷。中印雙方至今未有作出回應。<br />\n<br />\n美媒表示，雙方用石頭、木棍等拳打腳踢，數名印軍受傷，由直升機運走救治，而解放軍也有受傷。網傳影片顯示，多名印度軍人在存在主權爭議的班公錯湖邊路上，猛烈砸爛偵察車，將一名疑似解放軍按倒在地，拳打腳踢。期間疑有人用普通話大叫「救命」。該名躺在地上的士兵頭破血流，被印度軍人帶走。<br />\n<br />\n有中國網民在微博發文稱，「此事很快通過兩軍的前線會晤解決了，但幾天後印軍繼續擴大事件，捂不住了」、「之後引發了班公湖大戰，印軍被我軍（解放軍）打傷72人」。另有印度媒體早前報道稱，中國在班公湖的巡邏艇數量增加3倍，已同印度部署在該湖45公里西端的巡邏艇數量相當"},{"pid":"07ba6f4abd46ae52bfdfca151d045066f6dece59","tid":2044781,"uid":55089,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-31T10:23:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c728caf760cd1a3995d01e3e6696be5af9cf4a9","tid":2044781,"uid":27